history.content:
We have made some room in lab sessions and on the waitlists for EECS151, so a few more are enrolled now.  The waitlists were full for some time, so if you were interested in this class but couldn't get in, please add yourself to the waitlist. 

We will be able to accommodate everyone who is on the waitlist now, and some more.  The class enrollment is primarily limited by the lab capacity, and we may be able to add sections if the waitlists fill up now; adding more lab sections will be much less likely in August. 

The prerequisites are CS61C and EECS16A, btw.
